"layout: post\n"
"title: 'Unused Beans and Why We Remove Them'\n"
"date: 2021-09-23\n"
"tags: cdi arc \n"
"synopsis: Why does Quarkus detect and remove unused beans by default?\n"
"author: mkouba\n"
